HEADWORD: Lhasa
<hw>Lhasa</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The capital city of Tibet; it is the
sacred city of Lamaism.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Lassa, Lasa, capital of Tibet.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A breed of terrier having a long heavy coat raised
in Tibet as watchdogs; also called <altname>Lhasa
apso</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Lhasa apso.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

